<h1>SignalR Queue Demo</h1>

<p>
    Blazor Server implementation of the DASH 2.0 walk-in queue POC — the same three experiences as the
    Angular apps, self-encapsulated (shared code, no REST calls to the API; see docs/decisions.md).
</p>

<ul>
    <li><a href="checkin">Check In</a> — public kiosk check-in and document upload.</li>
    <li><a href="staff">Staff Console</a> — call-next/complete, document viewing (staff key required).</li>
    <li><a href="display">Queue Display</a> — public read-only waiting-room board.</li>
</ul>
